WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.495
Two complications change the clinical calculus.

00:00:02.495 --> 00:00:05.405
Sudden cardiac death accounts for up to

00:00:05.405 --> 00:00:08.316
fifteen percent of myocarditis mortality in young

00:00:08.316 --> 00:00:08.732
adults.

00:00:08.732 --> 00:00:11.642
Intracardiac thrombus forms in four to twelve

00:00:11.642 --> 00:00:12.889
percent of cases.

00:00:12.889 --> 00:00:15.800
Both can occur with preserved ejection fraction.
